    USAGE

        prova [modules] [options]

    OPTIONS

        -b     --browser    Publishes the tests on localhost:7559
        -i     --visit      Publishes the tests and visits automatically. PhantomJS required.
        -p     --port       Changes the default port number. [7559]

        -g     --grep       Run tests matching with given pattern
        -t     --timeout    Set test-case timeout in milliseconds [2000]

        -V     --no-vm      Run tests in normal context, instead of a custom VM context.
        -S     --kstack     Disables Prova's modifying stack trace for showing better stack traces.

        -j     --json       Output in JSON format.
        -c     --cp         Run as child process(es) paralelly.
        -C     --cs         Run as child process(es) serially.

        -v     --version    Show version and exit
        -h     --help       Show help and exit
